Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:49.53,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}引擎的嗚咽是默契的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.77,0:22:52.41,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在正是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.79,0:22:56.93,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}苟且之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:02.04,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快樂之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:06.78,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唯有菸草的煙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:12.78,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}縈繞身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:17.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰人都藏有自己的秘密
